%F A365692 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..floor(n/2)} binomial(n-k-1,k) * binomial(n+2*k+1,n-2*k) / (n+2*k+1).
%F A365692 D-finite with recurrence of order 16 (see link). - _Robert Israel_, May 18 2026
%o A365692 (PARI) a(n) = sum(k=0, n\2, binomial(n-k-1, k)*binomial(n+2*k+1, n-2*k)/(n+2*k+1));
